ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force Saint Christopher (St. Kitts) and Nevis FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the FEDERATION OF SAINT CHRISTOPHER (ST. KITTS) AND NEVIS FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed in Saint Kitts on 14 June 2010.
